<p>Second Div had a "hop over" in the vicinity of Lagnicourt reached the 3rd line but were compelled to retire; attacked again but this time reached &amp; held their objective; their casualties were very heavy, reports say 2000; ambulances also suffered heavy casualties among the bearers.</p>
<p>Saturday 5.5.17<br/>Sports continue in the horse transport line.  Entered for a few events but were unlucky not pulling off a prize.</p>
<p>Sunday 6.5.17<br/>Word through for us all to stand to in readiness to go out to the line.  7th F. Amb have had 39 casualties since the beginning of the month &amp; 14 F Amb 15. <br/>7th went over in 2nd wave of attack &amp; 14th 3rd wave.</p>
